WEBVTT

00:02.403 --> 00:03.769
OHH, YEAH!

00:03.771 --> 00:06.438
♪ POWERPUFF GIRLS
FIGHTING CRIME ♪

00:06.440 --> 00:09.041
♪ TO SAVE THE WORLD
BEFORE BEDTIME ♪

00:09.043 --> 00:11.510
♪ HERE'S THE TIME TO SHINE
WHEN YOU'RE FIGHTING CRIME ♪

00:11.512 --> 00:13.278
♪ POWER IT UP ♪
♪ WHO'S GOT THE POWER? ♪

00:13.280 --> 00:14.713
♪ WE GOT THE POWER ♪

00:14.715 --> 00:16.949
♪ THEY CAN DO THE WALK,
GONNA DO IT ALL ♪

00:16.951 --> 00:19.151
♪ WE DON'T QUIT ♪
♪ WHO'S GOT THE POWER? ♪

00:19.153 --> 00:20.786
♪ WE GOT THE POWER ♪

00:20.788 --> 00:23.288
OH! YEAH!

00:29.230 --> 00:31.563
Narrator:
AH, THE CITY OF TOWNSVILLE!

00:31.565 --> 00:33.665
A BRIGHT AND SHINING BEACON
OF --

00:33.667 --> 00:35.000
WHOA, TOO SHINY!

00:35.002 --> 00:37.469
WAIT A SECOND! WHAT'S THIS?!

00:41.308 --> 00:44.009
Packrat: SHINY!

00:44.011 --> 00:46.912
SHINY!

00:46.914 --> 00:49.081
SHINY!

00:49.083 --> 00:50.916
SHINY THINGS! SHINY THINGS!

00:50.918 --> 00:54.086
PACKRAT IS THE KING
OF SHINY THINGS! [ LAUGHS ]

00:54.088 --> 00:56.822
Narrator: [ SNIFFS ]
I SMELL A RAT --

00:56.824 --> 00:58.357
<i> PACK</i> RAT, THAT IS.

00:58.359 --> 01:00.926
OH! SO SHINY!

01:00.928 --> 01:03.362
RITA LOVES SHINY!

01:03.364 --> 01:06.098
HEY, PACKRAT,
TIME TO PACK IT UP!

01:06.100 --> 01:08.434
NO! THE SHINY IS MINE!

01:10.071 --> 01:12.271
OKAY, GIRLS,
THETA FORMATION!

01:12.273 --> 01:14.073
BUT THAT'S THE MEANEST
FORMATION.

01:14.075 --> 01:17.609
I DON'T WANT TO HURT 'EM.
THEY'RE JUST CUTE LITTLE MICES!

01:17.611 --> 01:18.877
[ GRUNTS ]

01:18.879 --> 01:20.412
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

01:20.414 --> 01:22.748
HEY, THERE.
WHATCHA GUYS SO UPSET ABOUT?

01:22.750 --> 01:24.416
[ GRUNTS ]
[ CLAY SHATTERING ]

01:24.418 --> 01:27.686
BUBBLES! STOP MESSING AROUND
AND START PUNCHING!

01:27.688 --> 01:31.090
OH, RITA,
YOU WILL LOVE THE NEW SHINY!

01:31.092 --> 01:32.257
[ LAUGHS ]

01:32.259 --> 01:34.560
GUYS, PACKRAT'S GETTING AWAY!

01:34.562 --> 01:37.129
HAVE YOU FORGOTTEN
THE THETA FORMATION?!

01:37.131 --> 01:40.132
[ GRUNTS ]

01:40.134 --> 01:41.800
[ GASPS ]
NO!

01:41.802 --> 01:43.969
AWW!
DON'T BE FRIGHTENED!

01:43.971 --> 01:45.604
YOU JUST NEED A HUG!

01:45.606 --> 01:48.807
AH.
NOW DON'T YOU FEEL BETTER?

01:48.809 --> 01:50.209
AAH!

01:50.211 --> 01:54.046
♪♪

01:54.048 --> 01:56.348
MUST SAVE THE SHINY!

02:00.154 --> 02:02.254
HERE I COME, RITA!

02:02.256 --> 02:04.223
[ RATS SQUEAKING ]

02:04.225 --> 02:06.558
SHINY FOR MY RITA!

02:06.560 --> 02:10.395
MY LITTLE RITA!
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:15.469 --> 02:17.402
[ GRUNTS ]
OUCHIE.

02:17.404 --> 02:19.972
BUBBLES, YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO
<i> PUNCH</i> THE BAD GUYS,

02:19.974 --> 02:21.173
NOT HUG 'EM.

02:21.175 --> 02:23.742
BUT HE WAS SO MAD.
AND FURRY.

02:23.744 --> 02:26.678
I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHY I BOTHER
GOING OVER THETA FORMATION

02:26.680 --> 02:28.647
IF NOBODY'S
GOING TO FOLLOW IT.

02:28.649 --> 02:31.116
POINT IS,
STOP BEING A WIMPY-BUTT!

02:31.118 --> 02:32.818
OUCHIE!

02:32.820 --> 02:34.019
ARE YOU OKAY?

02:34.021 --> 02:36.455
MY ARM HURTS REAL BAD!

02:36.457 --> 02:39.291
AW, PLEASE,
NOT LIKE IT'S BROKEN.

02:39.293 --> 02:40.692
YEP, IT'S BROKEN!
LOOKS LIKE

02:40.694 --> 02:42.995
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO WEAR
A CAST FOR A WHILE.

02:42.997 --> 02:46.632
GREAT.
NOW I REALLY<i> AM</i> A WIMPY-BUTT.

02:46.634 --> 02:48.600
Buttercup: TRUTH.
DON'T WORRY, BUBBLES.

02:48.602 --> 02:51.703
I SPECIALLY ENGINEERED THIS CAST
SO IT WON'T SLOW YOU DOWN!

02:51.705 --> 02:53.539
THIS BUTTON
ADJUSTS THE FITTING.

02:53.541 --> 02:55.874
THIS BUTTON ADJUSTS THE GRIP.
THIS IS FOR TRACTION.

02:55.876 --> 02:58.277
THIS ONE'S FOR TARGETING,
CONTRACTION, EXPANSION.

02:58.279 --> 03:00.145
AND THIS ONE MAKES...

03:00.147 --> 03:02.681
CAPPUCCINO!

03:02.683 --> 03:06.285
AH, THE TASTE OF VIENNA
ON A COLD WINTER MORNING.

03:06.287 --> 03:07.386
DELICIOUS.

03:07.388 --> 03:09.688
AWESOME!
I WANT A CAST, TOO.

03:09.690 --> 03:13.192
CASTS ARE ONLY FOR PEOPLE WHO
HAVE BROKEN BONES, BUTTERCUP.

03:13.194 --> 03:14.393
GOTCHA.

03:14.395 --> 03:15.894
Professor: BUTTERCUP...

03:15.896 --> 03:17.396
AW, MAN!

03:17.398 --> 03:19.698
BUBBLES, WHY DON'T YOU
GIVE IT A WHIRL?

03:19.700 --> 03:20.866
UM...

03:20.868 --> 03:21.967
[ GASPS ]

03:23.304 --> 03:24.670
AAH!

03:24.672 --> 03:26.738
UGH, THIS IS HOPELESS.

03:26.740 --> 03:29.841
I'LL ALWAYS BE A WIMPY-BUTT.

03:29.843 --> 03:32.244
[ Echoing ]<i> WIMPY-BUTT...</i>
<i> WIMPY-BUTT...</i>

03:32.246 --> 03:33.679
<i> WIMPY-BUTT...</i>

03:33.681 --> 03:36.481
COME ON, BUBBLES.
YOU ARE NOT A WIMPY-BUTT.

03:36.483 --> 03:38.417
YEAH, I'D CALL YOU
MORE OF A WIENER-BUTT.

03:38.419 --> 03:39.885
STILL A BUTT,
EITHER WAY.

03:39.887 --> 03:40.986
BUTTERCUP!

03:40.988 --> 03:42.521
[ RINGING, BUZZING ]

03:42.523 --> 03:44.089
WHAT'S THAT, MR. MAYOR?

03:44.091 --> 03:46.825
PACKRAT? NOT AGAIN.

03:46.827 --> 03:48.927
LET'S GO!

03:48.929 --> 03:51.096
COME ON, BUBBS!

03:51.098 --> 03:52.598
[ SIGHS ]

03:52.600 --> 03:55.200
SHINY THINGS! SHINY THINGS!

03:55.202 --> 03:56.401
[ HISSES ]

03:56.403 --> 03:58.237
STOP RIGHT THERE,
YOU DIRTY RAT!

03:58.239 --> 03:59.404
[ Chuckling ] NICE.

03:59.406 --> 04:01.406
NO! ATTACK!

04:01.408 --> 04:03.408
[ RATS SQUEAKING ]

04:03.410 --> 04:06.678
♪♪

04:08.849 --> 04:11.116
DUDE, HE'S GOING MEDIEVAL
ON US!

04:11.118 --> 04:12.918
[ LAUGHS ]

04:16.090 --> 04:17.956
[ WHIMPERS ]

04:21.362 --> 04:24.029
COME ON, BUBBLES!

04:24.031 --> 04:25.631
I DON'T KNOW!

04:27.735 --> 04:30.969
HEY!
NOBODY MESSES WITH MY SISTERS!

04:30.971 --> 04:32.871
[ GROWLS ]

04:32.873 --> 04:35.207
♪♪

04:35.209 --> 04:37.876
[ GASPS ]
UH-OH.

04:37.878 --> 04:39.478
[ SCREAMING ]

04:39.480 --> 04:42.948
[ WHISTLE! CRASH! ]

04:42.950 --> 04:45.317
BUBBLES,
THAT WAS SPECTACULAR!

04:45.319 --> 04:47.319
YEAH, I GUESS I DID IT!

04:47.321 --> 04:49.321
THIS ARM IS PRETTY GREAT,
AFTER ALL!

04:49.323 --> 04:51.156
WAY TO GO, BUBBS!

04:51.158 --> 04:52.424
HIGH FIVE!

04:52.426 --> 04:54.126
[ GRUNTS ]

04:54.128 --> 04:56.461
THAT PUNCH WAS...

04:56.463 --> 04:58.964
AWESOME!

04:58.966 --> 05:00.966
[ CAT MEOWS ]

05:00.968 --> 05:04.069
♪♪

05:07.641 --> 05:10.175
[ ARM BEEPING ]

05:10.177 --> 05:12.577
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

05:15.516 --> 05:16.748
[ BABBLES ]

05:16.750 --> 05:18.517
WELL, I GUESS
LUNCH BREAK'S OVER.

05:18.519 --> 05:21.820
♪♪

05:23.957 --> 05:25.924
[ ALL SCREAMING ]

05:28.028 --> 05:29.928
[ ALL SCREAMING ]

05:37.805 --> 05:39.538
BUT THE POLICE
COULDN'T CATCH THEM,

05:39.540 --> 05:42.207
SO I LAID DOWN
THE LONG ARM OF JUSTICE.

05:42.209 --> 05:43.709
I'M TALKING ABOUT ARMSIE.

05:43.711 --> 05:46.044
[ SCOFFS ]
YES, BUBBLES, WE KNOW.

05:46.046 --> 05:47.012
ARMSIE.

05:47.014 --> 05:49.181
OH, NO!
WE MISSED OUR STOP!

05:49.183 --> 05:51.249
DON'T WORRY.
I GOT THIS.

05:52.720 --> 05:54.886
[ KIDS SCREAMING ]

05:54.888 --> 05:58.557
OH, WHOA. THAT WAS A DOOZY.
[ ALL GROANING ]

05:58.559 --> 06:01.059
BUBBLES,
THAT WAS REALLY DANGEROUS.

06:01.061 --> 06:02.461
BUT WE MADE OUR STOP.

06:02.463 --> 06:04.029
IT JUST SEEMS LIKE
YOU MIGHT BE GETTING

06:04.031 --> 06:06.631
A LITTLE CARRIED AWAY
WITH THAT NEW ARM.

06:06.633 --> 06:08.467
HIS NAME IS ARMSIE!

06:08.469 --> 06:10.736
-WHATEVER!
-ARMSIE HELPS PEOPLE.

06:10.738 --> 06:13.572
BESIDES,
HE'S THE HAPPIEST DUDE AROUND!

06:13.574 --> 06:15.540
DOES HE LOOK DANGEROUS
TO YOU?

06:15.542 --> 06:18.143
[ Deep voice ]
HI, BLOSSOM!

06:18.145 --> 06:20.011
[ Normal voice ]
GOOD JOB, ARMSIE.

06:20.013 --> 06:23.315
YOU THINK BUBBLES EVER LISTENS
TO WHAT SHE'S SAYING?

06:23.317 --> 06:26.251
BUBBLES, JUST THE GIRL
I'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR.

06:26.253 --> 06:29.888
OH, HI, PROFESSOR. DO YOU NEED
ME AND ARMSIE TO DO SOMETHING --

06:29.890 --> 06:32.090
MAYBE DISH OUT
SOME STREET JUSTICE?

06:32.092 --> 06:35.193
I SAW A BUNCH OF DOORS OUTSIDE
THAT WEREN'T BROKEN YET.

06:35.195 --> 06:38.363
ACTUALLY, IT'S TIME
FOR THAT CAST TO COME OFF.

06:38.365 --> 06:39.431
WHAT?!

06:39.433 --> 06:41.867
THAT'S RIGHT.
IT'S BEEN SIX WEEKS.

06:41.869 --> 06:44.102
-YOU'RE ALL HEALED.
-NO!

06:44.104 --> 06:46.405
FINALLY!
THINGS CAN GET BACK TO NORMAL.

06:46.407 --> 06:50.175
AND YOU CAN STOP TREATING THAT
CAST LIKE IT'S A REAL FRIEND.

06:50.177 --> 06:51.176
WHAT?!

06:51.178 --> 06:54.780
I CANNOT BELIEVE
WHAT I AM HEARING TODAY!

06:54.782 --> 06:56.681
ARMSIE IS MY BEST FRIEND!

06:56.683 --> 06:58.884
YOU CAN'T TAKE HIM AWAY FROM ME!

06:58.886 --> 07:02.721
ASK YOURSELVES,
"WHAT IS FRIENDSHIP?"

07:02.723 --> 07:04.022
AH, HERE WE GO.

07:04.024 --> 07:05.957
IS IT THE SHIP
ATOP THE FRIEND SEA

07:05.959 --> 07:08.393
BOUNCING IN THE OCEAN
OVER WAVES,

07:08.395 --> 07:10.195
SAYING HI TO SEAGULLS,

07:10.197 --> 07:11.763
SOLVING MYSTERIES?

07:11.765 --> 07:13.965
OR IS IT A SUBMARINE,

07:13.967 --> 07:18.136
DIVING DEEPER AND DEEPER
INTO THE SEA OF UNDERSTANDING,

07:18.138 --> 07:20.705
YET ALSO STILL SAYING HI
TO SEAGULLS,

07:20.707 --> 07:22.774
WHO ARE IN
THEIR OWN SUBMARINE?

07:22.776 --> 07:24.309
AND, FURTHERMORE --

07:24.311 --> 07:27.646
BUBBLES, QUIT STALLING!
IT'S TIME TO TAKE THAT CAST OFF.

07:27.648 --> 07:29.481
NO!
YOU'RE JEALOUS!

07:29.483 --> 07:31.216
YOU'RE ALL JEALOUS!

07:32.820 --> 07:34.319
THAT WENT WELL.

07:34.321 --> 07:35.487
[ SIREN WAILING ]

07:35.489 --> 07:36.822
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

07:36.824 --> 07:38.657
HOW CAN THEY DO THIS?

07:38.659 --> 07:41.159
FIRST, THEY TELL ME
I'M TOO WEAK!

07:41.161 --> 07:44.729
AND THEN I GET ARMSIE,
AND THEY TELL ME I'M TOO STRONG!

07:44.731 --> 07:47.899
THEN THEY TELL ME
THAT I TALK TO MYSELF TOO MUCH.

07:47.901 --> 07:50.402
ARMSIE'S NOT DANGEROUS!

07:50.404 --> 07:53.171
[ DOG YELPS ]
HEY, FREE PUPPY!

07:53.173 --> 07:54.739
THEY'RE JUST JEALOUS!

07:54.741 --> 07:58.577
THEY'RE JUST ALL WIMPY-BUTTS!

07:58.579 --> 07:59.845
WIMPY-BUTTS!

07:59.847 --> 08:02.280
WIMPY-BUTTS!
[ GROWLING ]

08:02.282 --> 08:03.415
HEY, BUBBLES?

08:03.417 --> 08:06.151
I AM NOT A WIMPY-BUTT!

08:06.153 --> 08:09.254
♪♪

08:10.757 --> 08:13.859
NO, RITA!
YOU CAN'T BREAK UP WITH PACKRAT!

08:13.861 --> 08:16.595
YOU ARE MY LOVE!
[ RUMBLING ]

08:16.597 --> 08:18.697
HUH?

08:18.699 --> 08:22.000
RUN, RITA! SAVE YOURSELF!

08:24.671 --> 08:27.239
[ GROWLING ]

08:31.478 --> 08:36.081
MUST GET BIG SHINY FOR RITA!

08:41.955 --> 08:44.523
SHINIEST!

08:44.525 --> 08:47.392
DUDE, IS THAT PACKRAT?

08:47.394 --> 08:48.627
Packrat: SHINY!

08:48.629 --> 08:50.962
ALL RIGHT, GIRLS,
DELTA FORMATION!

08:50.964 --> 08:54.900
NO! ARMSIE AND I WILL
TAKE CARE OF THIS BY OURSELVES.

08:54.902 --> 08:58.069
♪ OH, YEAH! ♪

08:58.071 --> 08:59.170
[ GRUNTS ]

08:59.172 --> 09:01.473
[ GROWLS ]

09:01.475 --> 09:03.441
[ STRAINING ]

09:06.747 --> 09:08.680
-BUBBLES!
-BUBBLES!

09:08.682 --> 09:10.849
BUBBLES, ARE YOU OKAY?!

09:10.851 --> 09:12.317
-AAH!
-AAH!

09:12.319 --> 09:14.286
[ BOING! SPROING! BOING! ]

09:16.657 --> 09:18.590
BLOSSOM, BUTTERCUP!

09:18.592 --> 09:21.192
OH, NO.
THIS IS ALL MY FAULT.

09:21.194 --> 09:24.329
Packrat:
OOH! SHINY FOR RITA!

09:24.331 --> 09:25.697
I HATE TO DO THIS,

09:25.699 --> 09:29.768
BUT I'M JUST NOT THE SAME PERSON
WHEN I'M WITH YOU, ARMSIE.

09:29.770 --> 09:31.770
SOMETHING'S GOT TO CHANGE.

09:31.772 --> 09:34.739
ARMSIE, WE HAD SOME GOOD TIMES.

09:34.741 --> 09:38.209
YOU WERE MY RIGHT-HAND MAN --
ER, ARM.

09:38.211 --> 09:39.377
[ SIGHS ]

09:39.379 --> 09:41.279
OKAY.

09:41.281 --> 09:43.949
[ BEEPING ]

09:43.951 --> 09:45.116
AAH!

09:45.118 --> 09:46.952
SHINY!

09:46.954 --> 09:48.119
AAH!

09:48.121 --> 09:49.588
SHINY!

09:49.590 --> 09:52.958
-AAH!
-SHINY!

09:52.960 --> 09:55.860
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU NEED?
A HUG!

10:02.402 --> 10:04.970
Narrator: AND SO, ONCE AGAIN,
THE DAY IS SAVED,

10:04.972 --> 10:06.705
BUT AT WHAT COST?!

10:06.707 --> 10:08.773
[ SOBBING ]

10:08.775 --> 10:10.809
WAIT! WHAT?
OH, THERE'S MORE?

10:10.811 --> 10:14.713
[ BOTH COUGHING ]

10:14.715 --> 10:17.115
-BUBBLES?!
-THERE!

10:17.117 --> 10:19.484
BUBBLES!
ARE YOU OKAY?

10:19.486 --> 10:21.753
[ GRUNTS ]
I THINK SO.

10:21.755 --> 10:24.322
BUBBLES, THAT WAS...

10:24.324 --> 10:27.225
THE GREATEST THING
I'VE EVER SEEN!

10:27.227 --> 10:29.594
DEFINITELY ONE OF
OUR TOP THREE EXPLOSIONS.

10:29.596 --> 10:31.730
[ GIGGLES ]
THANKS.

10:31.732 --> 10:33.398
AND I'M SORRY.

10:33.400 --> 10:36.468
I SHOULDN'T HAVE BEEN
SO DEPENDENT ON ARMSIE.

10:36.470 --> 10:38.303
WELL, WE'RE SORRY, TOO.

10:38.305 --> 10:40.472
YEAH, YOU'RE NOT
A WIMPY-BUTT.

10:40.474 --> 10:41.506
LET'S GO HOME.

10:41.508 --> 10:44.175
[ CRUNCH ]
OW! MY LEG!

10:44.177 --> 10:45.143
SERIOUSLY?

10:45.145 --> 10:49.014
WE ARE NOT
GETTING YOU A CAST.

10:49.016 --> 10:50.649
WHAT IF WE CALL IT "LEGSY"?

10:50.651 --> 10:51.816
-NO!
-NO.

10:51.818 --> 10:52.917
"LEGOR"?

10:52.919 --> 10:53.952
-NO.
-NO.

10:53.954 --> 10:55.487
"LEGS LUTHOR"?

10:55.489 --> 10:58.623
-NO!
-NO!

10:58.625 --> 11:01.192
SHINY FOR RITA!

11:03.964 --> 11:05.463
♪ POWERPUFF GIRLS
FIGHTING CRIME ♪

11:05.465 --> 11:07.999
♪ SAVING THE WORLD
BEFORE BEDTIME ♪

11:08.001 --> 11:10.669
♪ BATTLING EVIL TOE-TO-TOE ♪

11:10.671 --> 11:14.606
♪ SAVING THE DAY,
A POWERPUFF GOAL ♪
